article.headline: Lehigh 59, Wagner 45
article.story: NEW YORK (AP) -- Jason Mgebroff scored 13 points and Joe Knight added 10 points and six assists to lead Lehigh to a 59-45 victory over Wagner on Sunday, the Seahawks' eighth straight loss. The Mountain Hawks (6-6) outscored Wagner 30-14 in the paint. Mark Porter had 15 points for the Seahawks (1-10). He left the game with an apparent sprained ankle with 12:40 to go and did not return. Sean Munson had two points and 12 rebounds for Wagner. After Wagner closed within three points on DeEarnest McLemore's jumper with 13:22 to go, Lehigh went on a 13-6 run to go up 48-38. Kyle Neptune closed the run with a jumper with 7:30 to play.
